# Both DOOM engines are unstable-only in the tree, so the stable-branch
# default would refuse to emerge them at all.
#
# Bare atoms, deliberately: an entry with no keyword accepts the unstable
# branch of whatever arch the machine runs. Writing ~amd64 here would pin
# the file to one architecture — the same reason VIDEO_CARDS never enters
# the repo.
games-fps/crispy-doom
games-engines/uzdoom
